sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant GoalDetail
    participant ProgressForm
    participant CalcService
    participant Store
    participant APIService
    participant Backend
    participant Database
    
    User->>GoalDetail: Navigate to goal detail page
    GoalDetail->>User: Display current progress: 15% (currentValue: 197)
    
    User->>ProgressForm: Click "Update Progress" button
    ProgressForm->>User: Display progress update form
    
    User->>ProgressForm: Enter new currentValue: 195
    User->>ProgressForm: Optionally add note: "Weekly weigh-in"
    User->>ProgressForm: Click "Save"
    
    ProgressForm->>ProgressForm: Validate input client-side
    
    alt Validation fails
        ProgressForm->>User: Show error message
        User->>ProgressForm: Correct value
    end
    
    ProgressForm->>Store: Optimistic update: updateProgressPending()
    Store->>Store: Update goal in store immediately
    Store->>User: Show loading state
    
    ProgressForm->>CalcService: Calculate new progress
    CalcService->>CalcService: Formula: ((195 - 200) / (180 - 200)) * 100 = 25%
    CalcService->>CalcService: Clamp progress: 0-100
    CalcService-->>ProgressForm: Return: { progress: 25%, isComplete: false }
    
    ProgressForm->>APIService: updateProgress(goalId, progress, currentValue, note)
    APIService->>APIService: Prepare request with progress entry
    APIService->>Backend: PATCH /api/goals/:id/progress
    
    Backend->>Database: Load goal from database
    Database-->>Backend: Goal data
    
    Backend->>Backend: Validate update (permissions, progress value, type-specific fields)
    Backend->>Backend: Recalculate progress (server-side validation)
    Backend->>Backend: Create progress history entry
    Backend->>Backend: Update goal: progress, currentValue, updatedAt, progressHistory
    
    alt Progress = 100%
        Backend->>Backend: Suggest completion
    end
    
    Backend->>Database: UPDATE goal + INSERT progress_history
    Database-->>Backend: Updated goal
    
    Backend-->>APIService: 200 OK with updated goal
    APIService->>APIService: Transform response
    APIService->>Store: updateProgressSuccess(goal)
    Store->>Store: Replace optimistic update with real data
    Store->>Store: Update goal in store
    Store->>Store: Update goal list cache
    
    GoalDetail->>User: Update progress bar: 25%
    GoalDetail->>User: Update progress percentage display: "25%"
    GoalDetail->>User: Add entry to progress history timeline
    GoalDetail->>User: Update type-specific displays (currentValue, progress bar)
    GoalDetail->>User: Show success message (optional)

